name: Graffitomania
description:
Graffitomania is a platform for Non-Fungible assets and Decentralized Finance (DeFi). 

Graffitomania GFM is a progressive deflationary DeFi and community driven token built on Binance smart chain (BSC). The main characteristic of our GFM token is that it has three functions that take place during each trade: Reflection, LP Acquisition and Burn.

Graffitomania combines RFI tokenomics and an auto-liquidity generating protocol.
